{"tid":1593382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荃灣女子墮行人天橋 昏迷送院","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:58:07.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"04c460660e5a0869045319157deb6d9ba8ae21b0","tid":1593382,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"荃灣港鐵站對開行人天橋，一名中年女子由天橋墮下，倒卧地面，昏迷送院，但仍有呼吸及脈搏。<br />\n<br />\n事發於早上10時04分，一名年約40至50歲女子攀過天橋1米高圍欄墮下，倒卧地面，救護員到場將她送往瑪嘉烈醫院救治。現場地面遺下一灘血迹，警方正調查其身份及墮橋原因。<br />\n<br />\n建立時間10:59<br />\n更新時間11:47<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1098925/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B-%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1098925%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9Gg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=9350b741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1098925%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B-%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A2&h=f8c9e6f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1098925/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B-%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2</a>"},{"pid":"c17c3872eae096dd8f825d33b62f3c8bb733f0cb","tid":1593382,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019